en: Sometimes I feel like I have no idea what I'm doing.
It's just, [pause]I'm not exactly the most experienced girl around when it comes to relationships, y'know?
I'm sure you're doing just fine!
Aye! Just do what comes naturally. Like riding a bike! ..[pause].
Except, y'know, if the bike transformed into {first_tape_description} sometimes... and also {player}'s the bike.
It's okay! As one energetic newcomer kindly informed me, being just a little bit 'cringe' is actually quite an endearing trait!
In the lands to the Far East, this concept is known as 'Gap M-'
You [wave amp=20 freq=10]really[/wave] gotta stop letting that kid lead you around.
I see the line between what's base and 'based' is rather thin indeed.
Well. Looks like [wave amp=20 freq=10]someone's[/wave] certainly caught up on their twenty-first century youth vernacular and colloquialisms.
Et si j'ai des croutes à manger? Vous pensez vraiment je suis né pour un petit pain?
Ne me donne pas une bombe et dis-moi de 'lâche pas la patate'! Tu me prends pour une valise?

column3: you okay? What was that about?
